Description:
Gencoa is a UK-based manufacturing firm, supplying magnetron sputtering components and sputter-based solutions for the vacuum thin film deposition industry. Gencoa's manufactured components provide enabling technology for many state-of-the-art thin film coating processes.

Gencoa have more than 20 years experience in delivering products for the thin film industry, and the range of products includes:
-	Optix process gas monitoring system for analysis and process monitoring of PVD/PACVD systems;
-	Rectangular planar magnetrons;
-	Circular planar magnetrons;
-	GRS rotatable magnetrons with end blocks for cantilever or drop-in mounting styles;
-	Speedflo reactive gas process controllers;
-	Plasma sources

As a business, Gencoa's experience in the industrial sputter process spans three decades, and has led to production-proven designs for many applications. These include semi-conductor, web, DVD, photovoltaic, reflectors, hard/deco coating and displays.

Gencoa also provide process setup support and optimization, process development, and sub-contract simulation services.

Local representatives are in place in Europe, Asia and North America. For up-to-date worldwide contact details, visit http://www.gencoa.com/worldwide-contacts

