The Striboil anti-wear nano-additive is a product of nanotechnologies which allows to significantly reduce mechanical friction losses and ensures fail- free operation of equipment, extends the service life of lubricants and fine filters. It also has anti-oxidant and detergent characteristics, making it possible to reduce the number of traditional oils and additives needed for the operation, and therefore cut lubricant costs. The nano-additive treatment does not require a stopover of the equipment and is made in the regular operation mode. Another important thing is that the use of the nano-additive does not require a higher qualification of the service personnel.

The advantages:
- increases the mechanism's service life by 1.5-2;
- reduces petrol and oil lubricants consumption by 10-20%; 
- reduces electricity consumption by 17%;
- decreases vibration level by 20-30%;
- reduces CO2 and other gases emission by 30-50%;

Method of application:
The amount of nano-additive for treatment of a unit is determined by the amount of oil applied. 15 ml of the product would be enough for 3-6 liters of oil. When the amount of oil in the unit is higher, the amount of the product increases proportionally. The treatment itself does not require special qualification. The nano-modifier is injected into the oil neck or the oil opening during the operation. It's essential that the unit continues the operation for some time in order to form a strong film modified by nanoparticles.

Example:
The effect after car engine treatment can be observed after 60-80 kilometers. After the next oil change in the treated unit, the Striboil efficiency IS NOT decreased. Repeated treatment by the product is required after another 100 - 150 thousand kilometers.
Product description and package:
Dark green suspension of a liquid lubricant and slurry of highly dispersed minerals. 
а) suspension
б) lubricant (for bearings)

Die Konvergenz und Integration der Nanotechnologie wird als neue Chance bzw. Notwendigkeit gesehen, welche eine enge Zusammenarbeit zwischen gewerblichen/industriellen Anwendern der Nanotechnologie, Produzenten von Nanotechnologieprodukten und Forschungseinrichtungen im Bereich der Nanotechnologieforschung bzw. der unterschiedlichen Wissensdisziplinen der Nanotechnologie erfordert.

Die Vernetzung und Kooperation einer umsetzungsorientierten Forschung im Bereich der Nanotechnologie ist - neben der Förderung von kooperativen Projekten zwischen Industrie und Wissenschaft - in Netzwerken und Plattformen ein Schlüsselelement zur erfolgreichen Umsetzung einer österreichischen Nano-Strategie.

Auch gilt es, die Potentiale der Nanotechnologie für Unternehmen zu erschließen.

Die strategischen Ziele der Plattform nanoNET.at definieren sich zukünftig wie folgt:

- die Wissensbasis und Kompetenzen für in Österreich relevanten Anwendungsfeldern zu stärken;
- die Diffusion von technologischem Wissen und Stärkung der Kooperation zwischen Wissenschaft und Wirtschaft zu ermöglichen;
- die Interdisziplinarität zu stärken und
- die Unterstützung der Umsetzung von Nanotechnologien zu ermöglichen;
- den Zugang zu Know-how und Kooperationspartnern im Ausland zu ermöglichen und
- die internationale Sichtbarkeit zu erhöhen.

A Somatec é uma empresa 100% nacional, fundada em 1999, com reconhecida experiência no gerenciamento de energia elétrica. Além de sua expertise em redes elétricas, a Somatec também é responsável pela produção de seus próprios equipamentos, assegurando aos seus clientes um atendimento completo e eficiente, da fabricação à comercialização, garantido a melhor relação custo-benefício.Orientada para o mercado de consumidores de energia elétrica, a Somatec atua de forma exaustiva na busca de soluções tecnológicas para redução do consumo e estabilização desta commodity nos diversos segmentos de mercado. 

A Somatec foi eleita por unanimidade como a vencedora na categoria energia da 6ª edição do Concurso Acelera Startup realizado pela FIESP em 2015.

Nossa solução é PATENTEADA!

Benefícios aos Sistemas Eletroeletrônicos de Precisão
- Redução no consumo real de energia elétrica em kWh;
- Aumento da vida útil de equipamentos;
- Aumento da vida útil de lâmpadas;
